CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 30, 1965, pg. 28, reads: "Ready For Crucial Tilt - Here are the members of the Fifth Avenue High School basketball team who are expected to carry the major portion of the load when the Archers meet Schenley High School in a crucial City League battle, at the Pitt Field House on Friday afternoon. Left to right: Gregory Howard, Lee Miller, Bob Fleming, Melvin Jackson, Richard Brooks, James Morris, Kenny Reynolds and Cleveland Edwards. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Fifth Avenue High School basketball team, from left: Gregory Howard, Lee Miller, Bob Fleming, Melvin Jackson, Richard Brooks, James Morris, Kenny Reynolds, and Cleveland Edwards, posed in gymnasium
